服務創新與設計 Service Innovation & Design - 服務科學研究所 Institute of Service Science






 












Welcome關於我們 About Us系所成員 Faculty博士班 PhD碩士班 Masters課程模組 Course Modules科管院 CTM












 

課程模組 Course Modules‎ > ‎
  

服務創新與設計 Service Innovation & Design



模組目的Module Aim
The Service Innovation & Design (SID) module is intended for:1) Guiding students to develop new services from initial user research, ideation, prototyping, presenting new service concept, and value analyses.2) Learning how to apply the knowledge and skills of design in the context of new service development.3) Implementing service innovation in organizations and creating entrepreneurship opportunities.

課程名稱Courses

^服務設計Designing for services ^技術商品化實作Implementation of Technology commercialization^資訊服務理論與實務IT Service^社會創業Social entrepreneur^服務系統創新設計 Innovation & Design of Service System^學習環境設計Design of Learning Environment^進階傳播科技工作坊Advanced Communication Technology Workshop(NCTU)^使用者研究User Experience Research (NCTU) or ^使用者經驗設計專題Research of User Ecperience Desgn(NCTU)^設計質性研究Qualitative Research in Design(NCTU)^使用者中心互動介面設計User-centered Interaction Design(NCTU)* offered only in English^ offered only in Chinese

認證方法Certificate
學生必續修滿上列課程中的三門課才能拿到此模組的認證。To obtain a certificate in Service Innovation & Design, students must take at least three courses from the above list.申請服科所模組專長證明書 Apply for concentration certificate


